title: GE Power bags 2 orders worth Rs 775 crore from Jaiprakash Power Venture
description: GE Power India secured Rs 774.9 crore orders for D&E and wet FGDs from Jaiprakash Power Ventures for Nigrie and Bina plants with specified execution timelines.
